{"tid":1312702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭同中央又成功一步","createTime":"2019-07-13T14:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T07:03:50.000Z","uid":209282,"like":190,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f97e3c9b69e921188a8b8728f5f142f71b759a80","tid":1312702,"uid":209282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"大家每日守牆，每星期遊行<br />\n<br />\n開始對象變左同藍絲黑警對抗<br />\n<br />\n中共由建國開始玩大革命已經好識分化人民 等你地人民果層自己鬥批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家見到你地市民自己內耗，推班黑警出黎，黑警又無腦 唔識思考，毅進仔咁高人工 打埋佢自己老母都仲得，佢地唔care同市民作對架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後發生咩事都好，中央一句是林鄭決定，然後林鄭話黑警決定，然後盧偉聰話前線決定，然後成件事就無左架啦。 最後點打七你地 一定無差佬比人拉，雨傘就話拉七警，拉警棍延伸，今次？ 提都無提，影到打人又點呀？ 吹呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家都要集中返我地對抗緊係一個不公既政權，黑警藍絲次要架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6674fd1477302f4094ed7717a2f1bb70b74c83","tid":1312702,"uid":209282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c17b8ec34f3f27adc31fab0094898f69407ccc1","tid":1312702,"uid":209282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e400706cdd7736d903b6ec2d23bda4a3a89c1aff","tid":1312702,"uid":227975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"